---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import aboutImage from "../assets/aboutImage.png";
---

<section class="p-6 lg:p-12 xl:p-16 my-8" id="about-section">
  <Image
    src={aboutImage}
    alt="This is me with my daughter when she was a baby. It's honestly the best I'll ever look, so why update it?"
    loading="lazy"
    class="object-cover rounded-full mb-12 w-56 h-56 mx-auto md:mx-8"
  />
  <p
    class="max-w-[48ch] text-teal-950 dark:text-white text-balance first-letter:text-5xl first-letter:font-bold first-letter:mr-1 first-letter:float-left first-line:text-lg first-line:tracking-wide"
  >
    Hello, I&rsquo;m Travis and I like making stuff for the web. In other words,
    I specialize in crafting accessible, human-centered, digital experiences.
    However, something tells me you're not here to read a bunch of industry
    jargon, are you?
  </p>
</section>
